snippet.textDisplay: This song is leaving me with a mixed emotion. In the end, there is a crescendo missing, like what we see in coke studio in Pakistan. While I know this has been done so that it makes you want to listen to it again. And yes it’s doing that. And it’s good for more views. But then you know that orgasmic feeling you get when u end a song on a high. That is just missing. I hope the makers are reading this.

snippet.textDisplay:
Song beautifully sung by maithli and group. ❤️  she is a girl who is just making her way and is superb. 

I just wish I could hear the same song in the voice of Rekha Bharadwaj, Sunidhi Chauhan aur Sona Mahapatra. 

Maithli'S voice has an awesome classical touch and all but I miss the fun and emotion in the voice of Rekha ma'am, Sunidhi ma'am and sona ma'am along with the harkat which again is mixed with emotions 

Beyond the song, they add nazakat, emotion, modulation and a bit of even raw local feel which acts like icing on cake and not sung in the same tone, pitch, flat with harkat
